    {
      "id": "JLNGqiTtmg_M-Xa1qWqfA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2311.0895146186394,
      "y": -5333.611970443578,
      "width": 1017.6994018554688,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 90,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBo",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1951515874,
      "version": 648,
      "versionNonce": 1623442942,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1770473281495,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4. token bucket algo: \nKeep the total bucket size and refill rate.\nKeep two things, current size of tokens and also the last updated timestamp. \n\nThis info needs to be present in shared data structure: it will be redis shared across multiple nodes of \napi gateway.\nThe redis is updated with the total tokens, and last updated time stamp in single atomic opearation.\n\nMULTI\nHSET alice:bucket_tokens <newcount>\nHSET alice:lastUpdated <time>\nHSET alice:ExpireAfter 3600s\nEXEC",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4. token bucket algo: \nKeep the total bucket size and refill rate.\nKeep two things, current size of tokens and also the last updated timestamp. \n\nThis info needs to be present in shared data structure: it will be redis shared across multiple nodes of \napi gateway.\nThe redis is updated with the total tokens, and last updated time stamp in single atomic opearation.\n\nMULTI\nHSET alice:bucket_tokens <newcount>\nHSET alice:lastUpdated <time>\nHSET alice:ExpireAfter 3600s\nEXEC",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vjpIiA2QK5LE6Cfw7FA-Y",
